These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, juice, mirinda, soy-milk
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking juice is between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking coffee##2
5. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person drinking sprite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3   |    4    |  5  |   6   |   7   |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee | juice | sprite | iced-tea | almond-milk | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-2::.
There 7 different types of food: watermelon, garlic, peas, lemon, onion, blueberry, cherry
1. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
2. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
4. the person eating peas is between the person eating lemon and the person eating watermelon##2
5. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
6. the person eating peas is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4   |     5      |    6    |     7      |
| Food   | blueberry | cherry | watermelon | peas | lemon | garlic | onion |

