.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: disco, house, hip-hop, indie, classical, country, dubstep
1. the fan indie is on the right of the fan hip-hop##1
2. the fan country is on the right of the fan dubstep##1
3. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the fan disco##1
4. the fan country is on the right of the fan dubstep##1
5. the fan house is on the left of the fan disco##1
6. the fan classical is between the fan country and the fan house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | country | classical | house | disco | hip-hop | indie |

