.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: animation, mystery, drama, crime, musical, superhero, family
1. the person watching family movies is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching musical movies##2
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
6. the person watching family movies is in the middle##1
7. the person watching drama movies is the person watching drama movies##1
8. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3    |      4      |    5    |    6    |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | mystery | crime | family | musical | animation | drama |

