.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-2-17::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: august, april, september, january, june, march, february
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in august##2
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3  |     4      |   5    |    6    |   7    |
| Birthday   | august | february | march | january | june | april | september |

